Author: Alsamman M. Alsamman [aut, cre], Muhammad Adeel [aut]
Maintainer: Alsamman M. Alsamman <alsamman@omrf.org>
Description: Creates paired Manhattan plots with one inverted for visual comparison of 
    genome-wide association studies (GWAS) results. The package provides tools for 
    generating publication-quality visualizations that highlight genetic associations 
    across two datasets, with customizable labeling, significance thresholds, and 
    formatting options. Includes functionality for clustering SNPs based on genomic 
    distance and p-values.
